<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْحَدِيد<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص١١٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{هُوَ الْأَوَّلُ وَالْآخِرُ وَالظَّاهِرُ وَالْبَاطِنُ وَهُوَ بِكُلِّ شَيْءٍ عَلِيمٌ}</span> <span class="c4">[الحديد: ٣]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ يَحْيَى:</span> <span class="c3">{الظَّاهِرُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ عِلْمًا»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{وَالبَاطِنُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ عِلْمًا»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>[ش <span class="c2">(يحيى)</span> هو ابن زياد الفراء , المشهور بعلم النحو]<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>